},{"pid":"ab746aa8e396b16218d0aae241e4024ae114e2e4","tid":385023,"uid":142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:57:06.000Z","msg":"冇用sound card 開心使用中"},{"pid":"acd27728f0fbdf143c5f07433a23ed3fc1ce554a","tid":385023,"uid":46590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T22:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇用sound card 開心使用中</blockquote><br />\n用開Sound card真係接受唔到onboard<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d9c3653c70d125921f2803b69c71cf7629e437","tid":385023,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"隻牛夠唔夠電？我自從換左SSD同超左條ram之後有時都會咁，行返2133就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00079fbbb614a2d233d6e808f25638f7db932f48","tid":385023,"uid":46590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻牛夠唔夠電？我自從換左SSD同超左條ram之後有時都會咁，行返2133就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻牛係V550，應該夠吧～？<br />\n但我一唔插PCI-E就冇事哦～<br />\n同埋應該唔關sound card事，試過插其他PCI-E周邊就會咁樣～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a154575162c3f7b4a28f4f2a917cb7cd70c1a560","tid":385023,"uid":78178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人會用到佢個pcie（即係好短個個）來插其他周邊？<br />\n我插咗個sound card 係pcie，宜家boot幾會boot2次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始按power制後會著機3秒到就熄，等2-3秒先正常著入Windows！<br />\n我check過係個pcie周邊問題，蚊咗佢就冇哩個問題～我試過插其他pcie周邊都係一樣～即係唔關個sound card事～<br />\n有冇人會咁樣？定係我塊板有問題？<br />\n<br />\nhelp~~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用crosshair vi hero都係咁，一超ram斷電再開機就會咁，但普通重新開機就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c285cca09a552d71ccd8a401d923c2b162f2a8b1","tid":385023,"uid":46590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有人會用到佢個pcie（即係好短個個）來插其他周邊？<br />\n我插咗個sound card 係pcie，宜家boot幾會boot2次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始按power制後會著機3秒到就熄，等2-3秒先正常著入Windows！<br />\n我check過係個pcie周邊問題，蚊咗佢就冇哩個問題～我試過插其他pcie周邊都係一樣～即係唔關個sound card事～<br />\n有冇人會咁樣？定係我塊板有問題？<br />\n<br />\nhelp~~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用crosshair vi hero都係咁，一超ram斷電再開機就會咁，但普通重新開機就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唯有等新BIOS啦～～～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}